This project is based on the Snowflake Connector for Google Cloud Dataplex,
originally developed by Google LLC as part of the cloud-dataplex project:
https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/cloud-dataplex/tree/main/managed-connectivity/community-contributed-connectors/snowflake-connector

Original work Copyright 2024 Google LLC, licensed under Apache License 2.0.

Modifications include:
- Horizon governance metadata extraction (tags, tag references)
- INFORMATION_SCHEMA.TAG_REFERENCES for real-time tag data
- Data type mapping with fallbacks for semi-structured types
- Cloud Workflows pipeline definition with error handling
- Secret Manager credential integration
